Class PriceHistory

  • java.lang.Object
    • api.PriceHistory
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    TdaPriceHistory

    public class PriceHistory
extends Object
    A simple container for an indefinite number of price instances. Currently supports only one symbol request at a time.

    Kyle
